Raspberry White Chocolate Yogurt Cookies
Tangy raspberry yogurt cookies with white chocolate chips
classic
Fruity, Chocolate, Soft

INGREDIENTS:
2 3/4 cups all-purpose flour
3/8 cup butter
6 oz raspberry yogurt
1/4 cup brown sugar
1/2 cup white sugar
1 egg
1 tsp baking soda
1/2 tsp salt
1 tsp vanilla extract
3/4 cup white chocolate chips

INSTRUCTIONS:
Preheat oven to 350Â°F. Line baking sheets with parchment paper
Beat butter, yogurt and sugars until well combined
Add egg and vanilla; beat until well blended
Add flour, baking soda and salt; beat until combined
Stir in white chocolate chips
Drop tablespoon-sized portions 2 inches apart on sheets
Bake 12-14 minutes until edges are set
Cool on baking sheet 5 minutes before removing